data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: This may be a picture of a pair of sisters. They have Asian faces and tanned skin. The older sister wore her hair braided with braids, and her hair is black and shiny. The younger sister also has black hair and shows a shy smile to the camera. They are all dressed in pink. It seems that adults like to dress up girls in pink because pink makes people look more lovely. They seem to be in good relationships, and their parents must have educated them well. They may have a very harmonious family environment. （95 字）
